
why data vizualization?

- easy understanding of data
- it saves more time because we can quickly analyze the data.
- for story telling
- data quality check

python based viz libraries
===========================

matplotlib - more customization on my graph/chart
seaborn - for beautification purpose
plotly - to create interactive charts

on what basis should i need to choose between the chart

1. univariate analysis      | to understand the quality of one feature                      | count plot, histogram, box plot, pie chart
                            |                                                               |
2. bivariate analysis       | to understand the quality/relationship between two features   | bar plot, scatter plot
                            |                                                               |
3. multivariate analysis    | to understand the relationship between more than 2 features   | pair plot, heat map, line plot






